					<li>Automatic task association</li>
					<li>Idle time detection</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon">üé≤</div>
				<h2>Monte Carlo Forecasting</h2>
				<p>Make data-driven predictions using sophisticated Monte Carlo simulations. Transform historical data into accurate forecasts with confidence intervals.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Historical data analysis</li>
					<li>Confidence interval calculations</li>
					<li>Risk assessment</li>
					<li>Scenario modeling</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon">üìä</div>
				<h2>Team Analytics</h2>
				<p>Gain deep insights into your team's performance with comprehensive analytics. Identify bottlenecks, optimize workflows, and make informed decisions.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Velocity tracking</li>
					<li>Bottleneck identification</li>
					<li>Capacity planning</li>
					<li>Performance trends</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="feature">
				<div class="feature-icon">üîÑ</div>
				<h2>JIRA Integration</h2>
				<p>Integrate seamlessly with your existing JIRA workflow. Automatically sync tasks, time logs, and updates between Narthbugz and JIRA.</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Automatic task syncing</li>
					<li>Time log synchronization</li>
					<li>Status updates</li>
					<li>Custom field mapping</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0 0 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		line-height: 1.1;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.feature {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
	}

	.feature:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #111827;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		color: #4b5563;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		color: #4b5563;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.container {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
